org.deeplearning4j.ui.stats

Class StatsListener

  • java.lang.Object
    • org.deeplearning4j.ui.stats.BaseStatsListener
      • org.deeplearning4j.ui.stats.StatsListener
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    java.io.Serializable, java.lang.Cloneable, RoutingIterationListener, TrainingListener

    public class StatsListener
extends BaseStatsListener
    StatsListener: a general purpose listener for collecting and reporting system and model information.

    Stats are collected and passed on to a StatsStorageRouter - for example, for storage and/or displaying in the UI, use InMemoryStatsStorage or FileStatsStorage.
